data.description: Beautifully remodeled Lake home only 5.4 miles to interstate access. Home features: Open floor plan with hardwood flooring throughout main level living area and wood wall accent features. Kitchen has newer cabinets with granite countertops and eat in bar area. Decorative fireplace in living room with French doors to massive screen porch as well as open deck area looking over lake, perfect for entertaining. Master suite has double vanity sinks, tub and large walk in tile shower as well as ex large walk in closet. Far end of home was converted to large guest suite or use as man cave/ game room. Full walk out basement could easily be finished out for additional bedroom or living space. 3 car carport & circle drive as well as pull around vehicle access to waterfront. Seasonal water but has access year around on Ryan's Creek easy walk to water with swim pier. As close as you will find to Shopping, Cullman City & Interstate. Use as Commercial use on this home as well, gateway to Smith Lake.
